          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5905580-lysergius?shelf=psychology-and-psychiatry">psychology-and-psychiatry</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3775578653" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14689947215779701129">This is a mammoth tome, best approached slowly. It is no less than an attempt to explain the behaviour of crowds, which it does by reference to a mass of anthropological and psychological sources. It is not an easy read, but having finally finished it it would seem to have been worthwhile.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3775578653">
